dynamicCode/
**/dynamicCode/

# Generated meshes and geometry copied by Allrun
**/constant/polyMesh/
**/constant/extendedFeatureEdgeMesh/
**/constant/triSurface/*.obj
**/constant/triSurface/*.obj.gz
**/constant/triSurface/*.eMesh
**/cellToRegion
**/constant/cellTable
**/constant/boundaryRegion

# Demo2 is a FEM-mode import case and currently keeps its reference mesh.
!demo2/constant/polyMesh/
!demo2/constant/polyMesh/**
!demo2/demo2B/constant/polyMesh/
!demo2/demo2B/constant/polyMesh/**

# CalculiX generated result files
**/spooles.out
**/*.12d
**/*.cvg
**/*.dat
**/*.frd
**/*.sta

